import user from '../views/UserModule/mock/user.js'
import upload from '../views/UserModule/mock/upload.js'
import code from '../views/CodeModule/mock/code.js'
import area from '../views/DictModule/mock/Area.js'
import data from '../views/DictModule/mock/Data.js'
import matl from '../views/MatlModule/mock/materials.js'
import report from '../views/ReportModule/mock/report.js'
import Mock from 'mockjs'
import table from '../views/TableModule/Mock/Table.js'
import ShellGlobal from '../views/ShellGlobalModule/Mock/ShellGlobal.js'
Mock.setup({
    timeout: '500-600'
});
export default {
    ...user,
    ...upload,
    ...code,
    ...area,
    ...data,
    ...matl,
    ...report,
    ...table,
    ...ShellGlobal
}
